{"tid":1943172,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Feather & Bones 老闆剪爛防疫街站","createTime":"2020-03-25T13:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T05:15:59.000Z","uid":287629,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"36cc7f2052423547616776670ac3fdc49ec18aef","tid":1943172,"uid":287629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:26:25.000Z","msg":"From 區講員facebook:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/113061346712567/posts/225993328752701/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F113061346712567%2Fposts%2F225993328752701%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4YZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=b24178e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/113061346712567/posts/225993328752701/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【洗街消毒，派搓手液，仲要被個無口罩廢佬剪海報】<br />\n<br />\n剛剛完街站，講返一下剛才情況<br />\n<br />\n1）由於有確診個案在feather  ＆ bone 樓上的瑧璈（Bonhemian House），所以我要去處理。今日街上已消毒，我已經將搓手液送到瑧璈管理處，有需要的住戶可以索取。唔夠可再問我地。大廈管理公司亦\b已進行消毒1<br />\n<br />\n同時，真係多謝 城寨  早前捐出幾百枝搓手液，以及口罩，及各樣應急物資，讓我地區居民受惠。<br />\n<br />\n2） 我做做下街站，咁 Feather &amp; Bone 個老闆就走出來撕爛我的武漢肺炎海報，都仲唔夠，再入返去拎埋把較剪出來剪我個易拉架索帶，我當然去阻止。可惜佢身型比較大，我無法阻止佢剪爛我啲野，好彩只係條索帶。<br />\n<br />\n然後就比佢不斷叫我fuck off，真係個種毫無內容的就咁不斷叫我fuck off，話條街個地方係佢咁喎。我話我唔係針對佢間舖，我唔會介意同佢傾。但佢樓上真係有確診，要通知街坊。可惜佢根本唔會聽，一咪要我走，仲話會搞鳩我。所以要警察介入，我都備左案先。<br />\n<br />\n爛左幾張海報同埋索帶，我無大礙。�<br />\n<br />\n你生意唔好，就去嘈林鄭，嘈下點解一早唔封關啦。<br />\n<br />\n廢佬無分國界，仲要唔帶口罩<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味<br />\n<br />\n同埋生意有差吖， 荃灣西分店啲人多到.."},{"pid":"9d0ebae666483b03096dcf78b64e3679d41525e0","tid":1943172,"uid":116723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134990463a537d2a67bf344619639aeed7b099c1","tid":1943172,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:33:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"181fb53e5b5948c0125056e25a3363cdee876a5d","tid":1943172,"uid":312242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:35:22.000Z","msg":"一個硬物塞落佢個頭度, 一條鎖匙插盲佢對眼"},{"pid":"dd16c79cbddf23df7b3be22a21785117b6b30210","tid":1943172,"uid":58863,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:57:59.000Z","msg":"去GOOGLE俾1星"},{"pid":"ea856d5688ae2bdb0253eeb0ab92421c764587e9","tid":1943172,"uid":81756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:04:21.000Z","msg":"係咪想人幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />消毒咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢老驚中肺炎人之常情姐"},{"pid":"d341c9f5d8a1003c9005ac00b37ea4dff6bcfbe6","tid":1943172,"uid":43936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:04:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c5775cadd3c365c888f811c0a06c75b9a1e043cb","tid":1943172,"uid":119271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:09:08.000Z","msg":"推 大家順手比個google評分"},{"pid":"039106ce486773555ec945b4d156840e88e36208","tid":1943172,"uid":97,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:09:17.000Z","msg":"推！ 永不錄用"},{"pid":"7ccfff291ad1c8d7364f4ef38017d43d1e8af599","tid":1943172,"uid":261773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:11:12.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"048d6271122fc7b2576ccd8b3270395458314920","tid":1943172,"uid":125553,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/25/221145_de374235e7b843ee0af44ddcf874d731.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F25%2F221145_de374235e7b843ee0af44ddcf874d731.jpeg&h=bfde3655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#黃店的重要性"},{"pid":"cfcde72e0a4b2290e9c5d1f20b71da8fe1001670","tid":1943172,"uid":97,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"afdb9b11abb79c949167a3f709b86ff0388ceb8